# 🇬🇧 English

## 🎯 Overview
This project is a complete **Football Match Prediction System** featuring:

- User predictions  
- Count predictions per outcome  
- Admin panel to set the real match result  
- Lottery among correct predictors  
- Create new matches  
- Change team names and flags  
- CSV export  
- Secure CSRF protection  
- Safe session handling  
- PDO database connection  

### 🖥 Admin Panel Preview
<img src="assets/admin-preview.png" width="100%" alt="Admin Panel Preview">

---

## ⚙️ Configuration (config.php)

### 🔐 Security
- CSRF token lifetime  
- Allowed MIME types  
- Max upload size  
- Secure session configuration  

### 🗄 Database
```php
PDO::ATTR_ERRMODE => PDO::ERRMODE_EXCEPTION;
PDO::ATTR_DEFAULT_FETCH_MODE => PDO::FETCH_ASSOC;
```

### 👤 Admin
```php
define('ADMIN_USER', 'admin');
define('ADMIN_PASS_HASH', password_hash('admin', PASSWORD_BCRYPT));
```

---

## 🛠 Project Structure
```plaintext
root
│── admin/
│── assets/
│── config/
│── css/
│── js/
│── index.php
│── README.md
```

